headline: 3 Dividend Growth Stocks to Buy in June and Hold Forever
summary: Prologis, MPLX, and McCormick are three dividend growth stocks with yields that are more than double the market average at recent prices.  Patient investors could receive double-digit percentage yields from these stocks down the road.  High-yield dividend stocks are great, but you know what's even better?
